{"word":"Millstone","slug":"millstone","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Millstone</b> Not to be taken in pledge<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=24&verse=6'>Deu 24:6</a><br/> Probably used in executions by drowning<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=18&verse=6'>Mat 18:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=41&chapter=9&verse=42'>Mar 9:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=17&verse=2'>Luk 17:2</a><br/> Abimelech killed by one being hurled upon him<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=9&verse=53'>Jdg 9:53</a><br/> Figurative of the hard heart<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=41&verse=24'>Job 41:24</a>"}]}